Royal Bafokeng Platinum Agrees Three-Year Wage Accord With NUM, Union Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-08-12T13:50:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/royal-bafokeng-platinum-agrees-three-year-wage-accord-with-num-union-says.html
     Aug. 12 (Bloomberg) --  Royal Bafokeng Platinum Ltd. (RBP)  has
agreed a three-year pay deal with  South Africa ’s National Union
of Mineworkers, the labor union said.  “Operators who are the lowest paid workers will receive a
10 percent increment in year one, a 9 percent increment in year
two and an 8 percent increment in year three,” the NUM said in
an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  